page.title: 20PEOPLE INVOLVED IN PROJECT
page.content: THIS PROJECT WAS COMPILED BY PUPILS OF PRIMARY 7 BRORA HIGH SCHOOL.THE NAMES OF THOSE TAKING PART WERE; TIMOTHY ALDERSON, STUART CAMPBELL, DEREK DUFFY, MERVYN FAASSEN-DE-HEER, JAMIE GRIFFITHS, SCOTT MACDONALD, STEVEN MACLEOD, STEPHEN MACLEOD, JAMES MILLER,JOHN MOODIE, BRUCE SUTHERLAND, DENIS SUTHERLAND, JOHNNIE SUTHERLAND, MICHAEL AITCHSON. AMANDA BROWN, TRACY MACLENNAN, RACHEL MACLEOD, ELAINE MILLER , LORNA MURRAY, AUDREY ROSS , MORAG SUTHERLAND, WENDY SUTHERLAND, JAYNE YOUNG, ANNE MARIE ROSS. WE WOULD ALSO LIKE TO THANK MR D GRIFFITHS,THE DOLL BRORA,MR B MACLEOD BRORA,SERGEANT R SMART BRORA, THE FISHERMEN OF BRORA,AND ALL THE INHABITANTS OF BRORA FOR THEIR INVALUABLE HELP.
